Package: bc-hash
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Parallel file-tree hashing CLI
 Walks directory trees and computes cryptographic / non-cryptographic
 digests (SHA-256, CRC32C, xxh3, xxh128) in parallel, with batched I/O
 via io_uring when available. On warm-cache corpora, typically
 1.5x-1.7x faster than find | xargs -P16 <tool> pipelines.
 .
 Supports the 'hash' and 'check' subcommands for computing digests
 and verifying previously-produced digest files, plus exclude/include
 path filters and adaptive single-thread vs multi-thread dispatch.
